high_descs: Go across to the TV stand across from the sofa.
Pick up the knife from the TV stand.
Turn right and go to the room beside the sofa, and head back to the tomato.
Turn to the tomato and slice the tomato.
Go to the doorway and turn left, then head to the red microwave
Place the knife in the microwave.
Head back to the room beside the sofa/
Pick up a slice of the tomato.
Turn left at the doorway, and turn right at the coffee table, then go across to the kitchen sink.
Place the tomato in the sink and rinse it, then pick it up.
Turn around to the red microwave.
Place the tomato in the microwave to the left side.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean slice of tomato in the microwave.

high_descs: Go straight and to the right to approach the TV stand against the wall.
Pick up the knife from the stand.
Turn around and go to the path to the left of the sofa, then take a right into the room.
Slice the tomato in the middle of the room.
Exit the room the way you came in, turn left, then right and go past the dining table into the kitchen area, then right again to the microwave ahead.
Place the knife in the microwave.
Return to the room you sliced the tomato in.
Pick up one slice of the tomato.
Return to the kitchen area, approaching the sink opposite the microwave.
Use the sink to rinse off the tomato slice.
Turn back to the microwave.
Place the tomato slice in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a washed tomato slice inside a microwave.

high_descs: Head straight to reach the TV stand on the right.
Pick up the knife from the TV stand.
Turn around to exit the living room and enter the room on the right and reach the table.
Cut the tomato on the table with the knife.
Turn around to exit the room and turn left and head to the microwave on the right.
Heat the knife in the microwave and take it out.
Head right and take a left turn to reach the room to face the table.
Pick up a slice of tomato from the table.
Turn around to exit the room and turn left and head to the sink on the right.
Wash the tomato slice in the sink and take it out.
Turn around to reach the microwave.
Put the slice of tomato in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put the washed slice of tomato in the microwave.
